        <p class="article-para-text">If this whole process is making you overthink everything, talk to someone. Ask a friend, older cousin, or a teacher. Even the local photocopy guy near the college usually knows what‚Äôs up.</p>
        <p class="article-para-text">This isn‚Äôt about being the smartest in the room ‚Äî it‚Äôs about getting through the process without messing up something small.</p>
  
